FBIS3-21777 "jptdd010__l94083" JPRS-TDD-94-010L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 7 March 1994 WEST EUROPE SPAIN `Operation Bread' Results in Seizure of 60 Kg of Heroin in Madrid LD2602210094 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 1900 GMT 26 Feb 94 LD2602210094 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] The Civil Guard have seized 60 kilos of high purity heroin in "Operation Bread" in Madrid. Three suspected members of an international drug-trafficking network were arrested. The drugs seized would have fetched over 1 billion pesetas on the market. In the town of Mojacar in Almeria province, the Civil Guard have seized 1,171 kilos of hashish resin, and arrested an Algerian national who is linked with the consignment.
